{"tid":1241203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出解放軍　比放手香港獨立更差　老解一出　國際金融中心即冇","createTime":"2019-06-18T15:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:22:26.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"939f4fd75d78b5ca61b0f27359dbf74da734efc0","tid":1241203,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1140982389901938688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1140982389901938688&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8Bzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=f41cdd28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1140982389901938688&h=15a9d0b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1140982389901938688</a><br />\n<br />\n如果說隔離軍營，會出兵（或從北方出兵），其實比放手香港獨立更差。香港獨立，中國還可以靠抹黑香港獨立解決，就像抹黑台灣民主一樣。你出兵，就立即失去國際金融中心，而且是在打貿易戰途中失去。這就攬炒了，而香港獨立後，其實還是會做中國生意，就像荷蘭獨立、美國獨立。"},{"pid":"861c33f482ccd43c94301525521fd622844b2e58","tid":1241203,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}